      "date": "2013-03-09 09:26:15.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: Verified\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.3/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/625e51c0-8898-11e2-83c6-52540035b04c).  Ran 12 tests.  No failures.",
