      },
      "date": "2013-03-13 20:52:16.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: I would prefer that you didn't submit this\n\nWhile it is true that LB_LINUX_MODPOST is only used in ldiskfs, the end result (AC_SUBST(MODPOST) and AC_SUBST(MODPOST_ARGS)) does not seem to be used anywhere, so it would be better to just delete this check entirely.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 1
    },
